# ── Rust build output ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
src/target/

# ── Generated overlay exports (contain user's personal media files) ───────────
# These are runtime outputs, not source code. Never commit.
cenas/
debug.log

# ── Old releases/cenas path (wrong output dir from early versions) ────────────
releases/cenas/

# ── Old Node.js artifacts (project fully migrated to pure Rust) ──────────────
node_modules/
package.json
package-lock.json
dist/

# ── Binary release executables (use GitHub Releases for distribution) ─────────
# Binary blobs inflate git history. Tag a release on GitHub instead.
releases/*.exe

# ── Old output folders (Node.js era) ─────────────────────────────────────────
output/
*.output/
overlay-*/
test-output/

# ── Old Tauri frontend (replaced by native egui GUI) ─────────────────────────
ui/

# ── Internal session docs (Claude/AI context, not for public repo) ────────────
alucard.txt
Eagora.txt
CLAUDE.md

# ── OS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Editor ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/settings.json
*.suo
*.user
